lf, spread out, dilated, widened."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b5-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He expatiated."},{"kind":"text","text":"One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tws~E fiY Ald~aAri","text_ar":"توسّع فِى الدَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu saAHapN ytws~E fiyhaA","text_ar":"لَهُ سَاحَةٌ يتوسّع فِيهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trk~H","text_ar":"تركّح"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He strode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in walking. ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tawas~aEuwA fiyhi Hat~aY A^aTolaquwhu","text_ar":"تَوَسَّعُوا فِيهِ حَتَّى اَطْلَقُوهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY ka*aA","text_ar":"عَلَى كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They extended its"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a word's)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"signification,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"amplified in respect of it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or rather,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took an extended range in using it, so that they applied it to such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(The lexicons, &c., passim.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tawas~aEa","text_ar":"تَوَسَّعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabaq~ara","text_ar":"تَبَقَّرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}